        <p>Another amazing beach you might like to visit is at <strong>Anthony Quinn Bay</strong>, with its clear vivid green and blue waters surrounded by a scenic bay. The bay is located just south of Rhodes City and north of Lindos, along the eastern coast of the island.</p>
